# Auto-Generated Tests

This directory contains tests automatically generated by the Evolution Agent
when running with `--auto-improve` mode.

## Review Process

1. Run `npm run monsters:evolve` to preview changes
2. Review generated `.ts` files
3. Edit tests to add specific assertions
4. Move approved tests to appropriate monster config

## Safety

- These tests are generated templates, not production-ready
- Always review before committing
- Delete tests that aren't useful

## Cleanup

```bash
# Remove all auto-generated tests
rm -rf tests/qa/monsters/auto-generated/*.ts
```
